{
  "texts": [
    "The events were presented in the prompt in random order.",
    "This prompt was developed iteratively by testing on a subset of 50 notes.",
    "The full prompt with few-shot examples can be found in Supplement B.We ran the LLM inference 4 times on each social history to achieve self-consistency.",
    "The value 4 was chosen to balance between accuracy and computation time on our hardware [36].",
    "Each run is independent (doesn't use information from prior runs) and may produce unique results due to the indeterministic nature of LLM inference when a temperature parameter is set to a non-zero value (we used a value of 0.7) [37]."
  ]
}